ere we stayed in California, &amp; after reading what they said about this hotel, we just had to write a review - it is so unfair. e.g. they said had to wait for elevators - we were up &amp; down heaps of times, &amp; never had to wait. Maybe that's cos we were there in April, not June/July/August? There are plenty of elevators, &amp; we can't imagine having to wait very long for one - whenever. Anyway, hope this helps future guests - it really is a wonderful hotel for the price &amp; location. Julia &amp; Keiji - Sydney Australia	
