Dec 3 2005 	Plaza Hotel and Casino - Dirty Dirty Dirty	The Plaza Hotel and Casino was horrible! Walking into the casino was like stepping into the Twilight Zone - - Visitors from the 60's never left. Every inch of the hotel smelled. The rooms were dark and dirty. The hotel carpet was sticky (even in the bedrooms). I lifted the sheets to find that the mattress was about 15 years old! The blankets and comforter had cigarette burns. The pillows were so old that the filling was smashed down to hard waifs. The walls were so thin we could hear everything going on in the next room - - squeeking bed springs in chorus with smokers cough. If you are looking for an inexpensive trip to the older side of the strip, try 4 Queens - - at least there you won't feel like you need to be sprayed down with pesticides.	
