nt. It all had this same weird tast though... We will surely go back to the Plaza. TAKE A CAB - not a shuttle. Shuttle took 1 1/2 hours, and a cab is just a few bucks more for about 1/4th the time. Better yet, take a limo with the loot you'll save and make it take the whole hour. Just remember to keep those expectations low when downtown and you will always be well rewarded...	
